                                    <dt>Schedule 5 Ordinary Allowable Itemized Deductions (Attach additional sheets, if necessary):</dt>
                                    <dd>Corporation, Partnership and Other Non-Individual with Mixed Income Subject to Multiple Income Tax Rates or with Income Subject to Special/Preferential Rate are mandated to use the itemized deduction. However, the use of itemized deductions shall not apply to juridical entities not allowed to claim any deductions (e.g., non-resident foreign international carriers).</dd>
